text: Sistine Rose Stallone (born June 27, 1998) is an American actress and model. She is known for her role as Nicole in the survival horror movie 47 Meters Down: Uncaged. She is the daughter of actor Sylvester Stallone. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:Models from Los Angeles Category:Actors from Los Angeles
